{"tid":1715962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方出動水警輪 接走中大中國學生","createTime":"2019-11-13T08:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:22:13.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aff8c887ab8668e15aae1d5f6b4faa980d728a96","tid":1715962,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2717038545025962/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2717038545025962%2F&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLabe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=5477997c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2717038545025962/</a><br />\n<br />\n【警方出動水警輪 接走中大中國學生】<br />\n<br />\n今早（11月13日）一批來自中國的中大生，基於安全理由打算搬離校園，但因為附近道路被嚴重阻塞，導致他們無法離開，於是聯絡警方尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n警方發聲明，指基於安全考慮及附近路面出現的堵路情況，決定調派水警輪協助該批學生前往安全地點。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-13-2019/57477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-13-2019%2F57477&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLabe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=78503b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-13-2019/57477</a><br />\n<br />\n#水警輪 #中大 #中國學生<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLabe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=9c8ed342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLabe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=be45624b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r